result.longName: Hang Tai Yue Group Holdings Limited

assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Hang Tai Yue Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the mobile internet, hospitality and related services, money lending, and assets investments businesses. The company's Mobile Internet Business segment is involved in the provision of IT services, maintenance services, and retail commerce through network media. Its Provision of Hospitality and Related Services in Australia segment focuses on the development of its hospitality business in Australia through Balgownie Estate Vineyard Resort and Spa Yarra Valley. The company's Money Lending Business segment provides unsecured loans to individual customers. Its Assets Investments Business segment engages in the investment in securities. The company also offers medical and administrative services; operates Walletku E-commerce, an online shopping platform; and Walletku Digital application, an electronic wallet for deposit of money, as well as offline and online payment to merchants. It has operations in Hong Kong, the People's Republic of China, Australia, and Indonesia. The company was formerly known as Interactive Entertainment China Cultural Technology Investments Limited and changed its name to Hang Tai Yue Group Holdings Limited in November 2018. Hang Tai Yue Group Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Jordan, Hong Kong.
